column3: Updated version: Removed `boost/lexical_cast.hpp` from `EXPECTED_BOOST_INCLUDES` now that #13383 has been merged. Added logic that notifies the operator when a previous dependency has been removed, asking for an update of `EXPECTED_BOOST_INCLUDES`.\n\n@laanwj Please re-review :-)

* #13230 (Simplify include analysis by enforcing the developer guide's include syntax)

If you consider this pull request important, please also help to review the conflicting pull requests. Ideally, start with the one that should be merged first.
@DrahtBot I'll simply rebase once one of them is merged :-)
